            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%BF%91%E6%9C%9F%E5%A9%B4%E5%B9%BC%E5%84%BF%E6%98%93%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E4%BA%BA%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E9%81%93%E5%90%88%E8%83%9E%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%BF%91%E6%9C%9F%E5%A9%B4%E5%B9%BC%E5%84%BF%E6%98%93%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E4%BA%BA%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E9%81%93%E5%90%88%E8%83%9E%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#近期婴幼儿易感染人呼吸道合胞病毒#</span></a>】冬春交替，各类呼吸道传染病高发。人呼吸道合胞病毒通过飞沫传播，主要表现为咳嗽、喘憋的症状。婴幼儿感染后，严重时会出现呼吸困难等症状。医生提醒，感染人呼吸道合胞病毒不可随意用药，家长要随时关注孩子的情况，如血氧低于95%，出现呕吐等要尽快就医。 <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4872243688439862" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hbd6kq4ygej61ko0vwb2902.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/M37k9DMLlx083mRXEX5S01041200KKOg0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1677271276&amp;ssig=6GiofNrQ9C&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/W8e9dxuUlx083mRXeZYs01041200p7xH0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1677271276&amp;ssig=jWXOs1taSq&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/tmnISKNilx083mRWOC3K01041200g00Y0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1677271276&amp;ssig=V2MvmgEqwt&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4872243688439862&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
