            <description><![CDATA[<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E9%95%BF%E6%9C%9F%E5%90%83%E5%A4%96%E5%8D%96%E6%98%93%E5%AF%BC%E8%87%B4%E5%BF%83%E8%82%8C%E6%A2%97%E6%AD%BB%23&amp;extparam=%23%E9%95%BF%E6%9C%9F%E5%90%83%E5%A4%96%E5%8D%96%E6%98%93%E5%AF%BC%E8%87%B4%E5%BF%83%E8%82%8C%E6%A2%97%E6%AD%BB%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#长期吃外卖易导致心肌梗死#</span></a><br><br>看到这个话题，相信宝子们和卫一样，又慌了<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[跪了]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_guile-a8a737d3a0.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[跪了]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_guile-a8a737d3a0.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[跪了]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_guile-a8a737d3a0.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><br><br>外卖食品油较重、盐偏高，长期吃外卖会导致高血脂，也会让血压、血糖更难控制，让冠心病向咱们这种年轻人靠近。<br><br>咱就是说，有没有一些简单又好吃的（懒人）食谱分享，让卫子这样的打工人一学就会的？<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[思考]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_sikao-ff9602dd08.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hbdgatzasyj2066065wet.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
